info.title: Ed-Tech Platform API
info.description: API for an educational technology platform, providing access to learning resources.

get.description: Retrieve lesson details based on a specific topic.

parameters.name: term
parameters.description: A search term or keyword related to the lesson content.

parameters.name: artifactTypes
parameters.description: The artifact type, Must be lesson.

parameters.name: field
parameters.description: The field to search. Must be title.

parameters.name: includeCourseSuggestionsOnly
parameters.description: Indicator to include course suggestions only. Must be true

parameters.name: pageSize
parameters.description: The page size for retrieval. Must be 3

parameters.name: primaryOrRelatedOrBoth
parameters.description: The content type to consider during search. Must be primary

parameters.name: shortLinks
parameters.description: Whether to use short URLs. Must be true

parameters.name: referrer
parameters.description: The referrer for the request. Must be FlexiGPT

200.description: A list of lessons matching the search term.

404.description: No lessons found matching the criteria.
